{"lastModified":1761131905054,"uri":"c::31479982513::vessel::d5cccc4b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Gulet","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Fethiye, Gocek, Marmaris, Kas, Demre \n\nThe luxury sailing yacht M/S Fortuna accommodates up to 14 passengers in 7 fully air-conditioned cabins, making it an ideal retreat for families and groups. Cabin options include: 1 Master Cabin (king bed, en-suite bath), 4 Cabins (queen beds), 2 Twin Cabins (two single beds in each).\n\nDesigned with classic craftsmanship and modern luxury, M/S Fortuna features spacious fore, side, and aft decks, offering outdoor dining, cushioned lounging areas, sun mattresses, and shaded spaces for relaxation. The elegant interior boasts high ceilings, wide corridors, a lounge with a stocked bar, cushioned seating, and an indoor dining area.\n\nA dedicated four-member crew ensures seamless service while maintaining separate living quarters for guest privacy.\n\nDining aboard M/S Fortuna is a culinary delight, crafted to satisfy even the most discerning palates. Our skilled chef masterfully prepares a menu that blends gourmet cuisine with authentic regional flavors, ensuring a truly memorable dining experience.","blueprint":{"name":"FORTUNA","images":["/media/media::image::c::31479982513::vessel::d5cccc4b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::651336d0-3635-11f0-b057-93302946d7a6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::31479982513::vessel::d5cccc4b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6c1f9b70-3636-11f0-9bdd-1716d3232c1e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::31479982513::vessel::d5cccc4b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::805826c0-3636-11f0-9bdd-1716d3232c1e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::31479982513::vessel::d5cccc4b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::63a30f90-3636-11f0-9bdd-1716d3232c1e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::31479982513::vessel::d5cccc4b-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c4616850-3635-11f0-92a6-bb250894b0c9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::imag